name: Listener Interspace
description: OLD SCHOOL MEETS NEW SCHOOL. “Listener Interspace” is the first ever cello AI generated art piece NFT with Assistant Principal Cello of the Seattle Symphony Nathan Chan and Machine Learning Artist, Developer, & Educator Lia Coleman. Inspired by the lightning speed of the crypto space and the chaotic glitchiness of life and technology, this original composition captures the excitement of NFTs and the endless possibilities of art and technology united. After all 10 editions are collected, holders of this NFT will be given exclusive access to a private streamed concert by Nathan Chan and a short lesson/Q&A from Lia Coleman on creating AI art at a mutually agreed upon time. After receiving NFT, email nathan@nathanchancello.com to verify ownership. @nathanchancello | @Lialialiacole
